Heard in third division, first district, at October term, 1939;opinion filed February 14, 1940.John E. Cassidy, Attorney General, for appellants; Earl B. Dickerson, William C. Clausen, James J. Teborek and Boring B. Moore, Assistant Attorneys General, of counsel; Charles J. Michal and John T. Murray, for appellee.
